                    <h3 style="width:100%;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;margin:0;padding-bottom:16px;font-weight:700;color:#28121F;line-height:20px;text-transform:capitalize;letter-spacing:-0.32px;text-align:left">South Africa&rsquo;s Home Affairs suspends officials over AI-generated references</h3>
